MOTION DOCKET

97-1880. Worthington City School Dist. Bd. of Edn. v. Franklin Cty. Bd. of Revision.

Board of Tax Appeals, No. 96-D-1218. This cause came on for further consideration upon the motion of appellee, Board of Education of Worthington City School District, to withdraw its motion for reconsideration filed on April 9, 1999. Upon consideration thereof,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion to withdraw the motion for reconsideration be, and hereby is, granted.
